window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Imagine a horse-powered world where magic is used for mending, making, and healing.</p> <p>Magical ability is rare, but Ky Vaux—a poor boy in a poor family—discovers he’s a mender one morning when he breaks a bowl and accidentally mends it.</p> <p>Can Ky’s gift of magic support Ky, his mother, and his sister while they attempt to escape from his abusive and alcoholic father?</p> <p>When Ky’s gift proves to be even more powerful than they had hoped, they can’t help but wonder if it’ll be able to take them farther than they had dreamed!</p>"; 
